    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example utilizes the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and lateral stability this platform is known for. While the car exhibits honest cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a recently serviced cooling system and valve adjustment. This is an excellent opportunity for an enthusiast to acquire a mechanically sound, analog performance icon that has been maintained with technical scrutiny.",
