      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained SUV offers a perfect balance of reliability and luxury. The exterior features a deep Obsidian Black finish that still holds a brilliant shine, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the Parchment leather cabin is exceptionally clean and strictly smoke-free; while the driver\u2019s seat shows light natural creasing, the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. Every feature, from the intuitive dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a complete service history and a recently installed set of high-performance all-season tires. It drives straight and true, providing a comfortable, vibration-free experience. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
