    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great in the driveway? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute. It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
