    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example retains its crisp throttle response and linear power delivery all the way to the 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power transfer. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. It sits on an upgraded suspension setup with Bilstein dampers, providing superior damping curves and roll stiffness. While the paint shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust and the rod bearings have been inspected. This is a driver-grade machine optimized for performance and mechanical longevity.",
